      "raw_text": "CHICAGO. April 1s.--If plans for\nINFLATED at a conference held at the\nBriggs house today go through the\nresult will be the permanent organi-\ncation of a national union OF railway\nclerks. The organization OF the clerks\nwill leave no branch of railroad en-\nployes unorganized. The movement\nhas been under way for some time\nand the new union will be affiliated\nwith the American Federation of\nLabor"
    }
